You the one that's been stealing
my magazines?

1696
01:44:25,800 --> 01:44:27,629
What would Charlie do?

1697
01:44:28,680 --> 01:44:30,509
[EXHALES]

1698
01:44:31,840 --> 01:44:34,102
Well, probably not this.

1699
01:44:55,960 --> 01:44:59,780
Listen, I'm sorry about Mickey.

1700
01:44:59,880 --> 01:45:01,311
Mickey.

1701
01:45:06,120 --> 01:45:10,544
Mickey could have taught all you
swinging beach bums a thing or two.

1702
01:45:12,360 --> 01:45:15,430
He was just so powerful.

1703
01:45:18,480 --> 01:45:22,107
Sometimes he could almost
make you feel invisible.

1704
01:45:25,600 --> 01:45:27,145
Fast.

1705
01:45:29,480 --> 01:45:30,866
Brutal.

1706
01:45:32,920 --> 01:45:36,342
Not what you'd call a considerate lover.

1707
01:45:39,840 --> 01:45:42,466
But we adored it about him.

1708
01:45:46,360 --> 01:45:47,666
Me...

1709
01:45:49,600 --> 01:45:52,863
and Sloane and Luz.

1710
01:45:58,280 --> 01:46:02,580
It's so nice to be made to feel
invisible that way sometimes.

1711
01:46:02,680 --> 01:46:04,544
DOC: Mm.

1712
01:46:05,080 --> 01:46:08,707
And guys just love
to hear shit like this.

1713
01:46:21,120 --> 01:46:24,064
He'd bring me to lunch in Beverly Hills.

1714
01:46:26,600 --> 01:46:29,500
One big hand wrapped
around my bare arm...

1715
01:46:29,600 --> 01:46:32,380
steering me blind
down those bright streets...

1716
01:46:32,480 --> 01:46:35,700
into some space
where it was dark and cool.

1717
01:46:35,800 --> 01:46:39,302
You couldn't smell any food,
only alcohol.

1718
01:46:41,120 --> 01:46:43,541
He had tables full of them.

1719
01:46:44,160 --> 01:46:45,989
They'd all be drinking...

1720
01:46:49,280 --> 01:46:52,941
in a room that could have been any size.

1721
01:46:55,080 --> 01:46:57,262
And they all knew Mickey.

1722
01:46:59,840 --> 01:47:02,307
They wanted, some of them...

1723
01:47:04,000 --> 01:47:06,023
to be Mickey.

1724
01:47:09,080 --> 01:47:13,185
He might as well have been
bringing me in on a leash.

1725
01:47:19,320 --> 01:47:21,660
He kept me in those micro-minidresses...

1726
01:47:21,760 --> 01:47:24,943
never allowing me
to wear anything underneath.

1727
01:47:31,840 --> 01:47:35,990
Just offering me up
to whoever wanted...

1728
01:47:36,440 --> 01:47:38,349
to stare...

1729
01:47:39,800 --> 01:47:41,390
or grab.

1730
01:47:43,560 --> 01:47:47,780
Sometimes, he'd fix me up
with some of his friends...

1731
01:47:47,880 --> 01:47:51,985
and I'd have to do whatever they wanted.

1732
01:47:52,520 --> 01:47:54,460
Why are you telling me this?

1733
01:47:54,560 --> 01:47:56,180
[GROANS]

1734
01:47:56,280 --> 01:47:58,542
I'm sorry, Doc.

1735
01:47:59,240 --> 01:48:01,104
Do you want me to stop?

1736
01:48:06,880 --> 01:48:10,180
If my girlfriend had run off
to be the bought-and-sold whore...

1737
01:48:10,280 --> 01:48:13,145
of some scumbag developer...

1738
01:48:16,320 --> 01:48:19,663
I'd just be so angry,
I don't know what I'd do.

1739
01:48:26,400 --> 01:48:27,865
No.

1740
01:48:29,880 --> 01:48:33,541
I'm even lying about that.
I know what I'd do.

1741
01:48:35,600 --> 01:48:38,943
If I had the faithless little bitch
over my lap like this...

1742
01:48:39,160 --> 01:48:43,788
[DOC GRUNTING AND SHASTA GASPING]

1743
01:49:00,960 --> 01:49:04,587
[BOTH GASPING]

1744
01:49:40,640 --> 01:49:43,471
This doesn't mean we're back together.

1745
01:49:45,880 --> 01:49:47,020
DOC: Mm.

1746
01:49:47,120 --> 01:49:48,790
Of course not.

1747
01:50:23,040 --> 01:50:26,986
You didn't get
this necklace up North, hmm?

1748
01:50:30,200 --> 01:50:32,462
I went on a boat ride.

1749
01:50:35,960 --> 01:50:38,028
Like a three-hour tour?

1750
01:50:42,000 --> 01:50:43,460
They told me...

1751
01:50:43,560 --> 01:50:48,348
I was precious cargo that couldn't
be insured because of inherent vice.

1752
01:50:49,400 --> 01:50:51,025
What's that?

1753
01:50:53,560 --> 01:50:55,150
I don't know.

1754
01:51:07,400 --> 01:51:09,343
[SHASTA MUMBLES]

1755
01:51:10,120 --> 01:51:12,348
- Hmm?
- Kiss me.

1756
01:51:34,960 --> 01:51:39,100
