1935
02:04:36,360 --> 02:04:39,820
Doper's ESP, Doc.

1936
02:04:39,920 --> 02:04:42,591
Doper's ESP.

1937
02:04:42,880 --> 02:04:46,621
[TIRES SCREECHING]

1938
